+---
+'xstate': major
+---
+
+Removed the ability to configure `input` within the implementations object. You no longer can do this:
+
+```ts
+createMachine(
+  {
+    invoke: {
+      src: 'child'
+    }
+  },
+  {
+    actors: {
+      child: {
+        src: childMachine,
+        input: 'foo'
+      }
+    }
+  }
+);
+```
+
+The `input` can only be provided within the config of the machine.
